Transitions:

    beamMeUp.c++		Pixel based (direct) transition

    CrossDissolve.c++		OpenGL based dissolve, using alpha blending

Filters:

    fade.c++			Pixel based (direct) fade with a dialog

    NoopConvolveFilter.c++	OpenGL based using convolution
    NoopDrawPixelsFilter.c++	OpenGL based using DrawPixels
    NoopTextureFilter.c++	OpengL based using texturing
